Package com.i2group.apollo.networksearchservice.transport

Contains classes for the services that perform network searches for items in the Analysis Repository and external data sources.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EntityNetworkSearchNode A kind of NetworkSearchNode that defines criteria that an Entity must match in order to appear in network search results.
ItemCountCondition A condition on a NetworkSearchNode that means a network of Items only matches a search if the number of Items at that position in the network meets the condition.
LinkNetworkSearchNode A kind of NetworkSearchNode that defines criteria that a Link must match in order to appear in network search results.
NetworkSearchNode A generic representation for EntityNetworkSearchNodes and LinkNetworkSearchNodes that provides the features that are common to both.
NetworkSearchNodeList Contains the NetworkSearchNodes that define the criteria and structure that the Items returned by a network search must match.
 

Enum Summary
ItemCountOperator Indicates the comparison that is performed when an ItemCountCondition is evaluated for a NetworkSearchNode.
 

Package com.i2group.apollo.networksearchservice.transport Description

Contains classes for the services that perform network searches for items in the Analysis Repository and external data sources.
